Class NPC

  • java.lang.Object
    • worldofzuul.NPC

  • public class NPC
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds all of the information regarding NPCs. It has methods for handling its inventory, both deleting and adding items

    • Constructor Detail

      • NPC

        public NPC(java.lang.String name,
           java.lang.String description,
           int rid,
           int pid,
           int conversationId,
           int chanceToMove)
        Constructor
        Parameters:
        name - of the NPC
        description - of the NPC
        rid - used to identify which items this NPC has to receive by the start of the game
        pid - used to tell where the NPC should be placed (on a moon or planet) at the start of the game
        conversationId - the first conversation id (which conversation file) the NPC should use at the start of the game
        chanceToMove - whether or not the NPC can move. 0 means completely no movement, 10 means certain of moving, in between means x/10 chance to move
